---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Ad Monetization Resources & Guides | AdBunny"
  description="Guides on remnant inventory monetization, banner ad optimization, and programmatic ad tech — from the team building AdBunny."
  keywords="remnant inventory guides, ad monetization resources, programmatic advertising blog"
>

<section class="pt-28 pb-12 max-md:pt-20">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[44rem]">
      <h1 class="font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-size:clamp(2.25rem,5vw,3.5rem)">Resources for smarter remnant inventory monetization</h1>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">Guides, explainers, and updates on remnant inventory, banner ad optimization, and where AI fits into modern ad monetization — for publishers and demand partners alike.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pb-20">
  <div class="max-w-[80rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="sr-only">Guides and resources</h2>
      <div class="py-6 px-4 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity cursor-pointer">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">Guide</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-1">What Is Remnant Ad Inventory? A Practical Guide for Publishers</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">Understand remnant inventory, how it differs from premium inventory, and why it's a revenue opportunity most publishers leave on the table.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-6 px-4 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity cursor-pointer" style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-border)">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">Analysis</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-1">Waterfall vs. Real-Time Optimization: What's Actually Costing You Revenue</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">Why static waterfalls leave money behind and how real-time AI optimization changes the math for remnant inventory.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-6 px-4 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity cursor-pointer" style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-border)">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">How-To</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-1">How to Monetize Unsold Ad Space Without Adding Ad-Ops Work</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">A practical walkthrough for publishers looking to generate revenue from unsold inventory without growing their team or toolchain.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-6 px-4 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity cursor-pointer" style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-border)">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">Guide</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-1">A Publisher's Guide to Fill Rate: What's Normal, What's Not</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">Benchmark your fill rate against industry standards and learn where remnant inventory optimization can make the biggest difference.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-6 px-4 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity cursor-pointer" style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-border)">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block" style="color:var(--color-text-tertiary)">Explainer</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-1">Single-Tag Integrations: Why Ad Tech Is Finally Getting Simpler</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-text-secondary)">How single-tag architectures are reducing engineering lift across ad tech and what that means for publisher monetization strategies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
